caption: I got takeout from Esquelito Taqueria today... Twice! It’s SO nice to have quality Mexican take out in the neighborhood that’s reasonably priced. The burritos and tacos are amazing - carne asada and chicken particularly. Flavor is fantastic, and portions are filling. Guac is fresh and salsas are delish. Esquelito is definitely going to be a mainstay on the family takeout rotation!
